                        <div class="dt-title" data-reactid=".p.2.0.0.3.0.0"><div class="dt-back" data-reactid=".p.2.0.0.3.0.0.0"></div><span data-reactid=".p.2.0.0.3.0.0.1">Knowing your fare</span></div><div class="issue-desc" data-reactid=".p.2.0.0.3.0.1">
                            <p>Fare for your Ola ride is calculated by adding the following -</p>
                            <p><span style="line-height: 1.5;">- </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;">Base Fare</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5;"> - A flat amount charged up to a particular distance or for the first few kms.&nbsp;</span><br><span style="line-height: 1.5;">- </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;">Distance Fare</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5;"> - The fare charged on per km travelled. Depending on the city, the Rate/Km may vary after a threshold distance or an extra charge may be applicable after a particular distance&nbsp;</span><br><span style="line-height: 1.5;">- </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;">Ride/Wait Time Fare</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5;"> -</span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">&nbsp;The fare charged on the total duration of the trip. thE The wait time fare on your ride includes any waiting time on the trip i.e. time taken to board the cab from the time driver arrived at the pickup location, time in traffic or at a traffic signal during the ride.</span></strong><br><span style="line-height: 1.5;">- </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;">Peak Pricing</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5;"> (if applicable)- Peak pricing might apply in some cities on standard fares depending on the time of booking. Peak pricing It is not a fixed charge and varies as per the demand for the cabs in your area.</span><br><span style="line-height: 1.5;">- </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;">Airport Charges</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5;"> (if applicable)</span><br><span style="line-height: 1.5;">- </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;">Taxes</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5;"> (as per the taxation rules)</span><br><span style="line-height: 1.5;">- </span><strong style="line-height: 1.5;">Toll and Parking Fee</strong><span style="line-height: 1.5;"> (if applicable)&nbsp;</span></p>
                            <p><strong>Note</strong> - <strong>Base Fare, Distance Fare </strong>and<strong> Ride/Wait Time Fare</strong> may vary depending on demand for cabs during that time and the cab category selected. You will be shown the revised rate card indicating the fare increase applicable on base fare, per km charge, and ride time.</p>
                            <p>You can view the rate card to understand the fare for your Ola ride. Click the <strong>Rate Card</strong> option available in the Ola app menu to check the fares for Ola rides in different cities.</p>
